    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
      
      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
          <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseOne">
            <h3>How to order?</h3>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse">
          <div class="accordion-inner">
            <h5>Order in 3 easy steps</h5>
            <ol>
                <li>Chose a product and click <strong>Order Now</strong></li>
                <li>Fill in the Order Form</li>
                <li>Ekont Express will notify you when your order has arrived</li>
            </ol>
            <hr />
            <p>
              Ordering products from <strong>www.jewellerybox.bg</strong> does not require a registration. After choosing your product click the <strong>Order Now</strong> button. You will be redirected to the Order page where you are required to fill in the form with your personal information and order details. Feel free to fill it in in either english or bulgarian language. Not all fields are required, however we value additional details. If the product has options to chose from, such as colors, you must specify them in the <strong>Message</strong> field in the order form. All orders are shipped within 3 working days.
            </p>
            <p>If you encounter any issues with your order or you have any other questions feel free to contact us at: <strong>office@jewellerybox.bg</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
          <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseTwo">
            <h4>What is a Price Class?</h4>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-body collapse">
          <div class="accordion-inner">
            <p>
              Products purchased from us are often used for gifts, which is why we created Price Class categories. They are designed to give you a sense of the price, yet the actual price is disguised - like any other gift.
            </p>
            <ol>
              <li><strong>Class A:</strong> 5 - 15 BGN</li>
              <li><strong>Class AA:</strong> 15 - 30 BGN</li>
              <li><strong>Class AA:</strong> 30 - 50 BGN</li>
              <li><strong>Class Lux:</strong> 50+ BGN</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseThree">
                <h4>What is included in the package?</h4>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-body collapse">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <p>
                Package contents vary from product to product. You can be sure that it is thoughtfully and carefully wrapped in a Jewellery Box. Some products include a cleaning cloth for silver, cloth jewellery bag, gift bag, or any other additions which would make you or your loved one smile.
              </p>
              <p>
                In some cases several products can be shown in one picture on the website. Bare in mind that the price is for 1 product. An exception is made for sets, such as earrings. The pictures we publish are soely aimed at representing the product.
              </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseFour">
