            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <p>
                Payment is made the moment you receive your order from Econt Express. The shipping price to an Econt office, according to your residential area varies with 5 BGN. for most cities in Bulgaria. For shipment outside Bulgaria contact us at: office@jewellerybox.bg
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Free shipping on orders <strong>Class AAA</strong> and <strong>Class Lux</strong>.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
