        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-body collapse">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <p>
                Not all products have a warranty. If the product you choose has one, it will be present on the page of the product and on the order page.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>You can return a purchased product</strong> and we will return your money, only if:
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>You return the product within 7 days of receiving it.</li>
                <li>You return the product in it's original condition.</li>
              </ol>
              <hr />
              <p>
                In case the return of the product is due to your mistake, you are obliged to cover the expenses associated with Econt Express. In case the mistake is ours, the responsibility to cover the expenses is also ours.
              </p>
              <small>
                Example: If you want to return a product because you wanted it with a blue stone, but you <strong>did not state it</strong> when ordering, it is your mistake. If you, however, stated it and we neglected your wish, it is our mistake and our responsibility.
              </small>
            </div>
        </div>
